::Prowl/Bloodystrike/Reptilica::

Prowl stumbles backwards as Iron Raptor bumps his hip. Even though the bump 
was soft, he was disoriented enough to nearly fall from it.

"No, I can fly," he says. He was obvioustly very dazed from the severed 
connection. Transforming into beast mode, he realizes his error as pain 
shoots through his body from his broken wing. He transforms back into robot 
mode, falling to his knees, his face green.

"Allright, maybe I do need some help," he admits, getting to his feet. He 
mounts Iron Raptor, his feet pressing on her sides, "Ok, let's go then, love."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Yelling in frustration, Bloodystrike and Reptilica fall along with Desmonus, 
finally hitting a wall at the end of a corridor. The base seems to stabalize, 
Bloodystrike getting up and seeing that it was Desmonus who fell with them.

"You allright?" he asks, his eyes sliding down her body. Next to him, 
Reptilica groaned, opening his eyes.
